## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="864c6-104">如果值<xref:System.Windows.Controls.GridSplitter.ResizeDirection%2A>屬性指定的資料列之間的空間會重新發佈，轉散發遵循這些指導方針：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="864c6-104">If the value of the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.GridSplitter.ResizeDirection%2A> property specifies that space is redistributed between rows, the redistribution follows these guidelines:</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="864c6-105">當<xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.VerticalAlignment%2A>屬性設定為<xref:System.Windows.VerticalAlignment.Top>，空間重新分配為指定的資料列之間<xref:System.Windows.Controls.GridSplitter>和高於該資料列的資料列。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="864c6-105">When the <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.VerticalAlignment%2A> property is set to <xref:System.Windows.VerticalAlignment.Top>, space is redistributed between the row that is specified for the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.GridSplitter> and the row that is above that row.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="864c6-106">當<xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.VerticalAlignment%2A>屬性設定為<xref:System.Windows.VerticalAlignment.Bottom>，空間重新分配為指定的資料列之間<xref:System.Windows.Controls.GridSplitter>和低於該資料列的資料列。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="864c6-106">When the <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.VerticalAlignment%2A> property is set to <xref:System.Windows.VerticalAlignment.Bottom>, space is redistributed between the row that is specified for the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.GridSplitter> and the row that is below that row.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="864c6-107">當<xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.VerticalAlignment%2A>屬性設定為<xref:System.Windows.VerticalAlignment.Center>，超過的資料列和低於指定的資料列的資料列之間重新分配間距<xref:System.Windows.Controls.GridSplitter>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="864c6-107">When the <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.VerticalAlignment%2A> property is set to <xref:System.Windows.VerticalAlignment.Center>, space is redistributed between the row that is above and the row that is below the row that is specified for the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.GridSplitter>.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="864c6-108">當<xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.VerticalAlignment%2A>屬性設定為<xref:System.Windows.VerticalAlignment.Stretch>，超過的資料列和低於指定的資料列的資料列之間重新分配間距<xref:System.Windows.Controls.GridSplitter>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="864c6-108">When the <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.VerticalAlignment%2A> property is set to <xref:System.Windows.VerticalAlignment.Stretch>, space is redistributed between the row that is above and the row that is below the row that is specified for the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.GridSplitter>.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="864c6-109">如果值<xref:System.Windows.Controls.GridSplitter.ResizeDirection%2A>屬性指定的空間會重新發佈的資料行之間，轉散發遵循這些指導方針：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="864c6-109">If the value of the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.GridSplitter.ResizeDirection%2A> property specifies that space is redistributed between columns, the redistribution follows these guidelines:</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="864c6-110">當<xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.HorizontalAlignment%2A>屬性設定為<xref:System.Windows.HorizontalAlignment.Left>，指定的資料行之間重新分配間距<xref:System.Windows.Controls.GridSplitter>和左邊的資料行。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="864c6-110">When the <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.HorizontalAlignment%2A> property is set to <xref:System.Windows.HorizontalAlignment.Left>, space is redistributed between the column that is specified for the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.GridSplitter> and the column that is to the left.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="864c6-111">當<xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.HorizontalAlignment%2A>屬性設定為<xref:System.Windows.HorizontalAlignment.Right>，指定資料行之間重新分配間距<xref:System.Windows.Controls.GridSplitter>和右邊資料行。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="864c6-111">When the <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.HorizontalAlignment%2A> property is set to <xref:System.Windows.HorizontalAlignment.Right>, space is redistributed between the column that is specified for the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.GridSplitter> and the column that is to the right.</span></span>  
  
